publisher			Ebonscale Games							
publish_time	 2015年12月14日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Dragonpath is a fast-paced top-down hack'n'slash RPG with abilities tied to equipment rather than classes. The game takes place in a broken underground realm inhabited by vicious monsters and few struggling remnants of civilization. Baptised in the dragon’s fire the champion yearns for vengeance; the master’s nemesis must fall. Master the ruthless combat, carve a bloody path through the depths of this ruined world and take the fight to the wretched being festering in the abyss.FeaturesCampaign with 15 levels divided into 4 chaptersSingleplayer and local 2-player co-op modesAbilities are tied to equipped items instead of classes20+ bosses and 30+ enemy types90+ items to find and plenty of enchants to modify themCustomizable hair styleDo you dare to walk the Dragonpath?						
